title: France: 'Get out of colonialism!' - Paris advocates Catalonia independence outside Spanish embassy
description:
Paris residents rallied outside the Spanish embassy in the French capital, Tuesday, in protest against the police brutality and the attitude of the Spanish administration towards the Catalan referendum for independence.
